%% Diagram: XState fetch machine — idle/loading/success/failure transitions
%% Type: state diagram
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> idle
    idle --> loading: FETCH(id)
    loading --> success: onDone (assign data)
    loading --> failure: onError (assign error)
    success --> loading: FETCH(id) refetch
    failure --> loading: RETRY

    note right of loading
        Invokes fromPromise(fetchUser).
        Only one in-flight invocation
        per machine instance.
    end note

    note right of success
        Impossible state combos like
        loading and error and data
        cannot be reached.
    end note
